 strategy NE where 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}_{1}^{*}=\left[\Pr(U),\Pr(M),\Pr(D)\right]=\left[\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2},0\right]$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}_{2}^{*}=\left[\Pr(L),\Pr(C),\Pr(R)\right]=\left[\frac{1}{3},\frac{2}{3},0\right]$
\end_inset

.
